Stephanie Braxton https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stephanie_Braxton 0 Stephanie Braxton (born December 11, 1944 in Boston, Massachusetts) is an American television writer, playwright and actress. She married Dan Hamilton in 1970, but they are divorced. She is the stepmother of Josh Hamilton.
